Class AlbumViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.AlbumViewer

  • public class AlbumViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    AlbumViewer is a class which allows the user to view the list of albums they currently have, and perform actions on these albums such as opening them and renaming them
    Author:
    Niles Ball, Scott Lahart
